1460","name":"List.intersperse_nil","line":1460,"kind":"theorem","docLink":"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.intersperse_nil","doc":""},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.intersperse_nil\"><span class=\"name\">List</span>.<span class=\"name\">intersperse_nil</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{α : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(sep : <span class=\"fn\">α</span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.intersperse\">List.intersperse</a> <span class=\"fn\">sep</span> <span class=\"fn\">[]</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <span class=\"fn\">[]</span></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/daa22187642d4cf6954c39a23eab20d8a8675416/src/Init/Data/List/Basic.lean#L1455-L1458","name":"List.intersperse","line":1455,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.intersperse","doc":"`O(|l|)`. `intersperse sep l` alternates `sep` and the elements of `l`:\n* `intersperse sep [] = []`\n* `intersperse sep [a] = [a]`\n* `intersperse sep [a, b] = [a, sep, b]`\n* `intersperse sep [a, b, c] = [a, sep, b, sep, c]`\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.intersperse\"><span class=\"name\">List</span>.<span class=\"name\">intersperse</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{α : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(sep : <span class=\"fn\">α</span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/daa22187642d4cf6954c39a23eab20d8a8675416/src/Init/Data/List/Basic.lean#L1436-L1438","name":"List.maximum?","line":1436,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.maximum?","doc":"Returns the largest element of the list, if it is not empty.\n* `[].maximum? = none`\n* `[4].maximum? = some 4`\n* `[1, 4, 2, 10, 6].maximum? = some 10`\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.maximum?\"><span class=\"name\">List</span>.<span class=\"name\">maximum?</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{α : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Max\">Max</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/daa22187642d4cf6954c39a23eab20d8a8675416/src/Init/Data/List/Basic.lean#L1424-L1426","name":"List.minimum?","line":1424,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.minimum?","doc":"Returns the smallest element of the list, if it is not empty.\n* `[].minimum? = none`\n* `[4].minimum? = some 4`\n* `[1, 4, 2, 10, 6].minimum? = some 1`\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.minimum?\"><span class=\"name\">List</span>.<span class=\"name\">minimum?</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{α : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Min\">Min</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/daa22187642d4cf6954c39a23eab20d8a8675416/src/Init/Data/List/Basic.lean#L1412-L1412","name":"List.enum_nil","line":1412,"kind":"theorem","docLink":"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.enum_nil","doc":""},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.enum_nil\"><span class=\"name\">List</span>.<span class=\"name\">enum_nil</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{α : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">[]</span>.enum</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <span class=\"fn\">[]</span></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/daa22187642d4cf6954c39a23eab20d8a8675416/src/Init/Data/List/Basic.lean#L1410-L1410","name":"List.enum","line":1410,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.enum","doc":"`O(|l|)`. `enum l` pairs up each element with its index in the list.\n* `enum [a, b, c] = [(0, a), (1, b), (2, c)]`\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.enum\"><span class=\"name\">List</span>.<span class=\"name\">enum</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{α : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">Nat</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Prod\">×</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span>)</span></span></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/daa22187642d4cf6954c39a23eab20d8a8675416/src/Init/Data/List/Basic.lean#L1402-L1402","name":"List.enumFrom_cons","line":1402,"kind":"theorem","docLink":"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.enumFrom_cons","doc":""},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.enumFrom_cons\"><span class=\"name\">List</span>.<span class=\"name\">enumFrom_cons</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\">∀ {<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1} {<span class=\"fn\">a</span> : <span class=\"fn\">α</span>} {<span class=\"fn\">as</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>} {<span class=\"fn\">i</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">Nat</a>}, <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.enumFrom\">List.enumFrom</a> <span class=\"fn\">i</span> <span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">a</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List.cons\">::</a> <span class=\"fn\">as</span>)</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">i</span>, <span class=\"fn\">a</span>)</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List.cons\">::</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.enumFrom\">List.enumFrom</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">i</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#HAdd.hAdd\">+</a> <span class=\"fn\">1</span>)</span> <span class=\"fn\">as</span></span></span></span></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/daa22187642d4cf6954c39a23eab20d8a8675416/src/Init/Data/List/Basic.lean#L1401-L1401","name":"List.enumFrom_nil","line":1401,"kind":"theorem","docLink":"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.enumFrom_nil","doc":""},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.enumFrom_nil\"><span class=\"name\">List</span>.<span class=\"name\">enumFrom_nil</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{α : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{i : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">Nat</a>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.enumFrom\">List.enumFrom</a> <span class=\"fn\">i</span> <span class=\"fn\">[]</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <span class=\"fn\">[]</span></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/daa22187642d4cf6954c39a23eab20d8a8675416/src/Init/Data/List/Basic.lean#L1397-L1399","name":"List.enumFrom","line":1397,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.enumFrom","doc":"`O(|l|)`. `enumFrom n l` is like `enum` but it allows you to specify the initial index.\n* `enumFrom 5 [a, b, c] = [(5, a), (6, b), (7, c)]`\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.enumFrom\"><span class=\"name\">List</span>.<span class=\"name\">enumFrom</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{α : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">Nat</a> → <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">Nat</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Prod\">×</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span>)</span></span></span></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/daa22187642d4cf6954c39a23eab20d8a8675416/src/Init/Data/List/Basic.lean#L1389-L1389","name":"List.iota_succ","line":1389,"kind":"theorem","docLink":"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.iota_succ","doc":""},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.iota_succ\"><span class=\"name\">List</span>.<span class=\"name\">iota_succ</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{i : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">Nat</a>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.iota\">List.iota</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">i</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#HAdd.hAdd\">+</a> <span class=\"fn\">1</span>)</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">i</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#HAdd.hAdd\">+</a> <span class=\"fn\">1</span>)</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List.cons\">::</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.iota\">List.iota</a> <span class=\"fn\">i</span></span></span></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/daa22187642d4cf6954c39a23eab20d8a8675416/src/Init/Data/List/Basic.lean#L1388-L1388","name":"List.iota_zero","line":1388,"kind":"theorem","docLink":"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.iota_zero","doc":""},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.iota_zero\"><span class=\"name\">List</span>.<span class=\"name\">iota_zero</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.iota\">List.iota</a> <span class=\"fn\">0</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <span class=\"fn\">[]</span></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/daa22187642d4cf6954c39a23eab20d8a8675416/src/Init/Data/List/Basic.lean#L1384-L1386","name":"List.iota","line":1384,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.iota","doc":"`O(n)`. `iota n` is the numbers from `1` to `n` inclusive, in decreasing order.\n* `iota 5 = [5, 4, 3, 2, 1]`\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.iota\"><span class=\"name\">List</span>.<span class=\"